metadata.name: Peptoshi 1
metadata.description: The Peptoshi Collection is a limited collection of 10 unique NFTs inspired by the protagonist of the Mithical Lore. Peptoshi the central figure in the realm of Yamata personifies the hopes and aspirations of the Mithical community.  He embarks on a journey across Yamata and unlocks secret knowledge possessed by each dynasty. As a result, mastering the ability to bend fire, water, wind, earth and the ether to his will. Each NFT symbolizes a key milestone moment in this journey.
